{"tid":1185092,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"諾基亞：5G訂單數量超越華為","createTime":"2019-06-04T05:06:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T16:43:41.000Z","uid":83518,"like":84,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"cc1867bd0a3d6ea47bc133d6ac90e56646f70eb9","tid":1185092,"uid":83518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:06:33.000Z","msg":"芬蘭電訊設備及服務商諾基亞(Nokia)表示，該公司的5G電訊設備在最近數周吸引更多買家興趣，幫助其訂單數量超越中國電訊設備商華為。<br />\n<br />\n諾基亞董事Federico Guillen稱，該公司目前獲得42份商用5G訂單，多於華為和愛立信(Ericsson)。由於美國挑起對中國設備的安全疑慮，諾基亞和愛立信的設備吸引力增強。<br />\n<br />\nGuillen對路透表示，現在量化仍言之尚早，惟最近數周觀察到有關發展趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n華為估計已敲定40份商用5G訂單。瑞典愛立信公開宣布達成19份合同。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1559617834994&amp;issue=20190604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1559617834994%26issue%3D20190604&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9Cgnr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=03406099\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1559617834994%26issue%3D20190604&h=96df3b9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1559617834994&amp;issue=20190604</a>"},{"pid":"ca724a62054426a9ac71cc778b2d8bdb56c82845","tid":1185092,"uid":159448,"like":3,"dislike":78,"score":-75,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:08:00.000Z","msg":"美國幾時制裁nokia"},{"pid":"93c4e5d0239752e0b97befcf2945c6688a1d4a55","tid":1185092,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca724a62054426a9ac71cc778b2d8bdb56c82845","tid":1185092,"uid":159448,"like":3,"dislike":78,"score":-75,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:08:00.000Z","msg":"美國幾時制裁nokia"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:09:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea8d4554fe6edb3d8350a06c024747c722ac4df","tid":1185092,"uid":80598,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"quote":{"pid":"ca724a62054426a9ac71cc778b2d8bdb56c82845","tid":1185092,"uid":159448,"l